<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://media.giphy.com/media/l0IyporbLKSE81CuI/giphy.gif);">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>The Art of Cocktail</h1>
    <p>Elegance in every sip</p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Make Your Drink</a>
  </div>
</div>
<h2>A place to discover and create the finest recipies of cocktails and mocktails.</h2>
